# Bull-11 Theme System

Complete centralized theme system for React Native app.

## Files Created (9 total)

### Core TypeScript Files (4)
1. colors.ts       - Color palette (80+ colors)
2. typography.ts   - Typography system (20+ text styles)
3. spacing.ts      - Spacing system (30+ values)
4. index.ts        - Main export with helpers

### Documentation (5)
1. README.md                  - Complete documentation
2. USAGE_EXAMPLES.md          - 10+ component examples
3. QUICK_REFERENCE.md         - Quick lookup cheat sheet
4. MIGRATION_EXAMPLE.md       - Before/after migration guide
5. IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md  - Complete implementation details

## Usage

```typescript
import { theme } from '@/src/core/theme';

// Use in styles
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    backgroundColor: theme.colors.background.default,
    padding: theme.spacing.padding.screen,
  },
  title: {
    ...theme.typography.textStyles.h1,
    color: theme.colors.text.primary,
  },
});
```

## Key Features
- Type-safe with full TypeScript support
- 80+ semantic colors
- 20+ predefined text styles
- 30+ spacing values
- Helper functions for dynamic colors
- Complete documentation with examples
- Ready for dark mode extension

Status: ✅ Ready for use
